  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and cook until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add curry powder, turmeric, cumin, salt, and pepper, and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add fish sauce and coconut milk, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and add fish fillets, covering the pan with a lid.",
    "Steam cook the fish for 8 minutes, or until cooked through.",
    "Serve the fish in the curry sauce, garnished with chopped cilantro if desired."
